<plot>Mystery. Destiny. Redemption. Sukiyaki. This musical retelling of the age-old classic takes place in a surreal world where houses have bagels for windows and trees sing scat. Little Red Jiving Hood draws its inspiration from the Ancient Mystical Bond between the Hunter and the Hunted - and the music of Betty Boop. In the interest of historical accuracy, Little Red Jiving Hood was filmed in the very same forest where the original incident actually took place.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?338411</url></doc>
